{"tid":1588687,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"和理非之最戴耀廷，正式「正名」係革命，唔係運動","createTime":"2019-09-23T02:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:12:10.000Z","uid":305299,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"734b63a6324f0db15e97e9e5c6fc590b30e3432b","tid":1588687,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"當和理非嘅最經典代表人物，戴耀廷，今日都不得不改口將五年前嘅79日「正名」為革命嘅時候，亦都自然代表今天嘅香港，唔理其他和理非<del>同藍絲</del>鐘意定願唔願意見到都好，必須承認「時代革命」係一個事實，而唔係反送中運動，而係一場我地香港人對抗全球最大獨裁政權嘅流水革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命，願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====內容=====<br />\n以前我會說「雨傘運動」，但我現在會認同應稱五年前發生的那79天為「雨傘革命」。若那不是「革命」，我解釋不了為何能在五年後的今天，在香港每天都發生著大家見到的事。那場革命雖未能改變制度，但肯定已是在人心中起了一場革命。或許我與我那一代人都是太保守，即使要向前走也不敢走得太大步。看見年青一代一往無前的決心，我怎能不羞愧呢？<br />\n=====傳送門=====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1192966217563804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F1192966217563804&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8ulyyBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=85f8819a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1192966217563804</a>"},{"pid":"bc3653717d14bfa095e7e414d1971e447258adb1","tid":1588687,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"11956c31b2e7a63261bec727d395d9b48740e1d1","tid":1588687,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a h